application.%26quot%3B%20After%20finding%20it%20I%20asked%20her%20to%20check%20the%20deadline.%20It%20turns%20out%20I%20was%20right%20about%20the%20time%20frame%2C%20since%20it%20was%20due%20in%20early%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20she%20was%20worried%20that%20she%20didn't%20have%20any%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteenage-ceo-juggling-high-school-and-business-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprior%20work%20experience%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20I%20reassured%20her%20that%20camps%20often%20value%20leadership%20roles%20at%20school%20and%20participation%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdont-join-extracurriculars-just-to-buff-up-college-application-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eextracurricular%20activities%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20her%20high%20GPA%20and%20academic%20awards%20could%20work%20in%20her%20favor.%20Plus%2C%20she%20did%20have%20experience%20looking%20after%20her%20younger%20cousins%2C%20which%20I%20assured%20her%20would%20count%20for%20something.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20filled%20out%20the%20application%2C%20she%20asked%20me%20for%20feedback%20about%20which%20activities%20to%20include%20(she%20does%20a%20lot!).%20After%20some%20discussion%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20highlight%20that%20she%20founded%20and%20serves%20as%20president%20of%20her%20school's%20environmental%20club%2C%20an%20activity%20that%20showed%20both%20her%20leadership%20skills%20and%20her%20love%20of%20the%20outdoors.%20Since%20the%20camp%20she%20applied%20to%20is%20an%20outdoor%20adventure%20camp%20that%20visits%20different%20parks%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20a%20perfect%20activity%20to%20feature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20got%20to%20the%20section%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-search-advice-ceo-on-references-using-recruiters-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereferences%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20it%20meant%20or%20who%20t