%20her%20friend%2C%20a%20retired%20fire%20department%20chief%2C%20and%20we%20walked%20the%20property%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22backyard%20of%20mountain%20home%20in%20colorado%20with%20trees%20everywhere%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6887e44b85e81483682ecf07%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMoore's%20dog%20in%20their%20backyard%20surrounded%20by%20trees.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Emily%20Moore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20out%20the%20changes%20we%20would%20likely%20need%20to%20make%3A%20updating%20the%20roof%20with%20fire-resistant%20shingles%2C%20adding%20a%20gravel%20barrier%2C%20taking%20down%20trees%2C%20and%20keeping%20wild%20grasses%20trimmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20to%20start%20by%20contacting%20a%20local%20nonprofit%2C%20Wildfire%20Partners%2C%20that%20assesses%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-pollution-colorado-wildfires-climate-threatening-access-to-the-outdoors-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewildfire%20risks%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20homeowners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20after%20closing%20on%20our%20dreamy%20mountain%20home%20in%20the%20winter%20of%202022%2C%20we%20scheduled%20our%20assessment.%20Since%20Wildfire%20Partners%20would%20not%20come%20until%20spring%2C%20and%20our%20yard%20was%20blanketed%20in%20a%20protective%20layer%20of%20snow%2C%20we%20shelved%20our%20concerns%20for%20the%20first%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fa732787-2f99-4ed3-96d6-2bde04058f3f%5C%22%3EWe%20faced%20a%20steep%20learning%20curve%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20assembled%20mood%20boards%20on%20Canva%2C%20scoured%20vintage%20rug%20resellers%2C%20and%20shopped%20for%20the%20perfect%20leather%20couch%20to%20complete%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhomeowner-divided-open-concept-living-area-partial-wall-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%