d%20how%20much%20of%20our%20planned%20wildfire%20mitigation%20budget%20would%20have%20to%20go%20toward%20these%20unexpected%20fixes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225aa81441-f32a-4e6f-ab28-ac4aa096dc3d%5C%22%3EThe%20scope%20of%20wildfire%20mitigation%20was%20larger%20than%20we%20expected%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22giant%20rainbow%20in%20colorado%20skies%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6887e54485e81483682ecf2b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221662%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMoore%20enjoyed%20beautiful%20rainbows%20during%20the%20spring.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Emily%20Moore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Wildfire%20Partners%20representative%20came%20out%20that%20spring%2C%20he%20tagged%20over%2030%20trees%20that%20we%20would%20need%20to%20cut%20down.%20His%2017-page%20assessment%20also%20involved%20trimming%20ladder%20fuels%20and%20fireproofing%20our%20house's%20exterior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20and%20when%20we%20completed%20our%20wildfire%20mitigation%20checklist%2C%20Wildfire%20Partners%20would%20come%20back%2C%20verify%20the%20work%2C%20and%20issue%20a%20certification.%20They%20would%20also%20match%20up%20to%20%242%2C000%20of%20arborist-related%20costs%2C%20but%20the%20rest%20would%20be%20on%20us%20to%20fund.%20The%20proposed%20scope%20of%20work%20would%20cost%20upwards%20of%20%2450%2C000%2C%20or%20several%20thousand%20less%20if%20you%20were%20able%20to%20DIY%20some%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20assessor%20assured%20us%20that%20most%20people%20take%20years%20to%20complete%20their%20checklists%20due%20to%20the%20time%2C%20money%2C%20and%20effort%20required.%20My%20partner%20and%20I%20debated%20our%20plan%20of%20approach%20and%20decided%20we%20would%20sleep%20better%20at%20night%20knowing%20we%20had%20taken%20all%20the%20necessary%20steps%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flos-angeles-wildfires-fireproof-my-home-roofs-siding-building-code-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprotect%20our%20home%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e16a6aab-1d3d-42b5-823c-5edb7df11f64%5C%22%3EA%20grassland%20fire%20put%20us%20on%20edge%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22woman%20with%20dog%20in%20colorado%20wilderness%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6887e593f748d8c055f668eb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMoore%20with%20their%20dog%20in%20their%20backyard%20with%20beautiful%20mountain%20views.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Emily%20Moore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20first%20(and%20only)%20summer%20in%20our%20dream%20home%2C%20we%20spent%20weekends%20working%20toward%20our%20certification.%20We%20felled%20dozens%20of%20trees%2C%20stacked%20logs%2C%20and%20gave%20them%20away.%20Friends%20pitched%20in%2C%20and%20a%20kind%20neighbor%20lent%20us%20chainsaws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgetty-villa-survives-palisades-fire-lessons-for-homeowners-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrimmed%20the%20wild%20grasses%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20covered%20our%20hillside.%20We%20installed%20a%20gravel%20barrier%20around%20the%20house%20to%20reduce%20the%20likelihood%20of%20a%20stray%20ember%20landing%20and%20catching%20flame.%20We%20interviewed%20contractors%20for%20more%20complex%20projects%2C%20like%20installing%20roofing%20and%20ledge%20flashing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20hard%20work%2C%20but%20it%20was%20rewarding.%20Before%20we%20knew%20it%2C%20we%20were%20only%20a%20few%20list%20items%20away%20from%20earning%20our%20certification%20and%20feeling%20accomplished.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22differnet%20colors%20and%20sizes%20of%20gravel%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6887e5b83d5881a51c1e2111%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20rocks%20that%20Moore%20and%20her%20husband%20chose%20for%20their%20gravel%20barrier%2C%20which%20added%20defensible%20space%20around%20their%20home.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Emily%20Moore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20one%20afternoon%2C%20a%20small%20wildfire%20broke%20out%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20neighborhood%20hill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20neighbor%20told%20us%20that%20someone%20operating%20a%20weedwhacker%20had%20nicked%20a%20rock%2C%20and%20the%20resulting%20sparks%20had%20started%20a%20brush%20fire.%20I%20watched%20smoke%20curl%20over%20the%20ridge%2C%20and%20refreshed%20my%20neighborhood%20message%20board%2C%20anxiously%20waiting%20to%20find%20out%20if%20we%20needed%20to%20evacuate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdads-version-retirement-shaped-relationship-with-work-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efirefighters%20acted%20swiftly%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20winds%20were%20not%20blowing%20that%20day%2C%20but%20this%20fire%20event%20brought%20back%20a%20devastating%20memory%20from%20just%20a%20few%20years%20prior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2030%2C%202021%2C%20a%20grass%20fire%20in%20Boulder%20County%20transformed%20into%20a%20suburban%20firestorm%2C%20fanned%20by%20wind%20gusts%20of%20over%20100%20miles%20per%20hour.%20In%20a%20matter%20of%20hours%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurviving-marshall-fire-colorado-what-los-angeles-should-expect-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarshall%20Fire%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20claimed%20two%20lives%20and%20over%201%2C000%20homes.%20People%20had%20minutes%20to%20evacuate.%20My%20partner%20and%20I%20read%20stories%20of%20neighbors%20knocking%20on%20doors%20to%20ensure%20no%20one%20was%20left%20behind%2C%20since%20there%20was%20no%20statewide%20alert%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWildfires%20are%20not%20only%20frightening%20because%20they%20are%20destructive.%20They%20are%20also%20infamously%20unpredictable.%20Just%20one%20ember%E2%80%94deposited%20by%20the%20wind%20onto%20a%20combustible%20ledge%E2%80%94could%20be%20the%20difference%20between%20avoiding%20disaster%20and%20losing%20your%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222216%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22sunset%20in%20colorado%20mountains%20in%20winter%20with%20snow%20all%20around%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6887e61e3d5881a51c1e211b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221662%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20stunning%20sunset%20view%20from%20Moore's%20backyard.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Emily%20Moore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20our%20friends%20at%20Wildfire%20Partners%20were%20so%20stringent%20about%20handing%20out%20certifications.%20Details%20that%20could%20appear%20insignificant%2C%20such%20as%20decking%20gaps%20or%20the%20type%20of%20mesh%20covering%20your%20vents%2C%20actually%20make%20a%20big%20difference.%20There%20was%20also%20hope%E2%80%94but%20not%20a%20promise%E2%80%94that%20the%20mitigations%20would%20help%20keep%20homes%20like%20ours%20insured.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227d3b5546-1d43-42cb-bba6-741b45773f23%5C%22%3EInsurance%20trends%20made%20us%20question%20our%20purchase%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20the%20insurance%20landscape%20began%20to%20change.%20We%20heard%20through%20the%20neighborhood%20grapevine%20that%20a%20neighbor's%20insurer%20had%20dropped%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20friend%20in%20another%20part%20of%20the%20state%20also%20lost%20her%20coverage.%20Finally%2C%20we%20read%20that%20State%20Farm%2C%20our%20insurer%2C%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-fire-insurance-coverage-cancellation-no-payout-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eno%20longer%20issue%20new%20home%20policies%20in%20California%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Could%20Colorado%20be%20next%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20occurred%20to%20us%20that%20our%20safety%20net%2C%20which%20we%20paid%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20annually%20to%20secure%2C%20might%20not%20be%20there%20for%20us%20when%20we%20needed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22woman%20in%20colorado%20wilderness%20in%20winter%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6887e707f748d8c055f66920%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22804%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMoore%20on%20a%20hike%20with%20their%20dog.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Emily%20Moore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20wondering%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20we%20lost%20everything.%20Would%20our%20insurer%20provide%20us%20enough%20to%20rebuild%20in%20place%3F%20Would%20we%20even%20want%20to%3F%20And%20in%20the%20absolute%20worst-case%20scenario%20possible%E2%80%94if%20a%20fire%20broke%20out%2C%20would%20a%20neighbor%20rescue%20our%20dog%20if%20we%20were%20unable%20to%20get%20to%20her%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20beers%2C%20the%20same%20neighbors%20who%20lent%20us%20yard%20tools%20recounted%20tales%20of%20their%20most%20recent%20evacuation.%20The%202020%20CalWood%20Fire%20had%20burned%20over%2010%2C000%20acres.%20On%20their%20wall%20hung%20a%20framed%20photo%20of%20the%20blaze%2C%20which%20had%20ripped%20through%20the%20foothills%20just%20across%20the%20canyon%20and%20leveled%2026%20structures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20in%20awe%20of%20their%20casual%20attitude%2C%20but%20they%20revealed%20important%20truths.%20We%20cannot%20control%20nature%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20many%20preventative%20checklists%20we%20complete.%20Also%2C%20we%20are%20far%20from%20experiencing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclimate-change-impacts-to-last-millennia-ipcc-report-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworst%20impacts%20of%20climate%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20as%20our%20government%20takes%20steps%20to%20halt%20climate%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommitting%20to%20life%20in%20a%20wi