3Emanifest%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20And%20then%20use%20AI%20to%20show%20me%20what%20my%20ideal%20life%20would%20look%20like%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20colleague%20Ana%20Altchek%20noticed%20the%20trend%20back%20in%20September.%20%26quot%3BUsers%20are%20sharing%20how%20AI%20has%20helped%20them%20enhance%20their%20traditional%20manifestation%20practices%2C%20such%20as%20visualizations%2C%20vision%20boards%2C%20positive%20affirmations%2C%20mantras%2C%20and%20rewiring%20negative%20beliefs%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20reported%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2229d4173b-f76d-4b28-a050-81bf7520fcfd%5C%22%3EChatGPT%20shows%20your%20dream%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20investigate%20for%20myself%2C%20and%20I%20found%20that%20people%20essentially%20prompt%20AI%20to%20create%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanifestation-journaling-latest-trend-to-combat-pandemic-fatigue-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estory%20about%20their%20dream%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20based%20on%20their%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20say%20your%20goals%20were%20to%20be%20rich%2C%20have%20flawless%20skin%2C%20snag%20a%20hunky%20husband%20and%20two%20kids%2C%20and%20live%20in%20a%20villa%20in%20Italy%20where%20you%20garden%20tomatoes.%20Enter%20those%20goals%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emanifest%3C%2Fem%3E%20them%2C%20if%20you%20will%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20it%20would%20whip%20up%20a%20story%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20you%20could%20use%20it%20to%20create%20an%20action%20plan%20to%20actually%20get%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20this%20out%20myself%2C%20asking%20ChatGPT%20to%20tell%20me%20a%20story%20about%20a%20day%20in%20my%20life%20in%20that%20Italian%20villa.%20I%20can't%20deny%20it%20delivered%20an%20appealing%20tale%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EThe%20sun%20slipped%20gently%20over%20the%20Tuscan%20hills%2C%20casting%20gold%20across%20the%20rolling%20vineyards%20and%20awakening%20Villa%20Rosabella%2C%20your%20sun-washed%20estate%20tucked%20among%20olive%20trees%20and%20cypress-lined%20roads.%20The%20sheets%20were%20linen%2C%20cool%20and%20crisp%2C%20and%20the%20smell%20of%20blooming%20jasmine%20drifted%20in%20through%20open%20French%20doors.%20You%20stretched%2C%20not%20a%20wrinkle%20on%20your%20face%2C%20your%20skin%20dewy%20and%20flawless%2C%20like%20you'd%20just%20walked%20out%20of%20a%20spa%20in%20Capri%20(because%20you%20had%20%E2%80%94%20last%20weekend).%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20I%20asked%20it%20to%20give%20me%20steps%20to%20achieve%20this%20dream%20life%2C%20things%20got%20a%20little%20wonky.%20Although%20it%20had%20some%20decent%20practical%20advice%20about%20how%20to%20achieve%20flawless%20skin%20(%26quot%3Bget%20a%20consultation%20with%20a%20top%20dermatologist%2C%26quot%3B)%20things%20got%20slightly%20more%20complicated%20when%20it%20came%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bbecoming%20rich%26quot%3B%20part%20of%20the%20dream.%20It%20suggested%20things%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BScale%20income%20to%20%24500K%2B%20annual%20revenue%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20...%20OK%2C%20sure%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20fair%2C%20had%20I%20given%20it%20slightly%20more%20specific%20goals%2C%20it%20might%20have%20come%20up%20with%20a%20better%20plan.%20But%20I%20need%20to%20admit%20my%20bias%20here%3A%20I'm%20not%20really%20%3Cem%3Einto%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20idea%20of%20manifesting.%20I'm%20happy%20for%20anyone%20who%20finds%20this%20useful%2C%20but%20it's%20just%20not%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20while%20back%2C%20I%20DM'ed%20some%20of%20the%20people%20I'd%20seen%20talking%20about%20this%20life%20hack%20on%20social%20media.%20A%20few%20of%20them%20told%20me%20they%20really%20did%20believe%20in%20the%20power%20of%20manifestation%20%E2%80%94%20and%20had%20clear%20life%20goals%20in%20mind.%20(I%20realized%20that%20these%20women%20were%20younger%20than%20I%20am%2C%20just%20starting%20out%20in%20their%20adult%20lives.%20Whereas%20I'm%20old%20enough%20that%20my%20only%20life%20goal%20is%20just%20to%20ride%20this%20thing%20out.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e0f0088d-ae86-4d36-9c37-6b1b505b0340%5C%22%3EManifesting%20on%20video%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20new%20twist%20to%20the%20AI%20manifestations%3A%20video.%20The%20New%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2025%2F07%2F26%2Fstyle%2Fai-vision-board-manifestation.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3EYork%20Times%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2025%2F07%2F26%2Fstyle%2Fai-vision-board-manifestation.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week%20that%20people%20are%20using%20tools%20like%20Runway%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkalshi-ad-filmmaker-veo-3-kicked-off-ai-studio-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20Veo%203%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20a%20tool%20called%20Freepik%20to%20enter%20a%20real%20image%20of%20themselves%20that's%20then%20used%20to%20illustrate%20a%20real%20(fake)%20life.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20could%20upload%20a%20picture%20of%20myself%2C%20and%20then%20have%20AI%20create%20a%20video%20of%20me%20sauntering%20around%20my%20Tuscan%20tomato%20grove.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20give%20it%20a%20try%2C%20so%20I%20tried%20to%20use%20Freepik%2C%20which%20one%20of%20the%20women%20interviewed%20by%20the%20Times%20used.%20But%20there%20was%20a%20catch%3A%20Freepik%20required%20a%20paid%20account%20to%20create%20video%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20there's%20no%20way%20I'm%20going%20to%20scale%20my%20income%20to%20%24500%2C000%20if%20I'm%20throwing%20it%20all%20away%20on%20AI%20tools%2C%20so%20I%20declined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22721%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22tomato%20plant%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68893c1ef748d8c055f67fa2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22861%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20one%20sad%20cherry%20tomato%20plant.%20I%20probably%20should've%20manifested%20more%20fertilizer.%3Cp%3EKatie%20Notopoulos%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPersonally%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20I%20want%20to%20see%20a%20video%20of%20myself%20in%20a%20dream%20life%2C%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20it%20would%20make%20me%20feel%20bad%20per%20se%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0or%20jealous%20of%20my%20dream%20AI%20self.%20And%20I'm%20not%20afraid%20that%20the%20AI%20version%20of%20me%20might%20come%20to%20life%20and%20murder%20and%20replace%20me.%20I%20simply%20do%20not%20wish%20to%20engage%20with%20such%20content.%20It%20just%20does%20not%20appeal%20to%20me%20at%20%3Cem%3Eall%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20I%20lack%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-develop-a-growth-mindset-according-to-psychology-researchers-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egrowth%20mindset%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20desire%20to%20truly%20improve%20my%20life.%20Perhaps%20I%20should%20be%20more%20open%20to%20AI%20manifesting!%20But%20also%2C%20I%20am%20happy%20to%20just%20use%20my%20imagination%2C%20and%20tend%20the%20one%20scraggly%20cherry%20tomato%20plant%20in%20my%20yard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-ai-manifest-dream-life-goals-why-explained-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753867802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6889332085e81483682ee4af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-ai-manifest-dream-life-goals-why-explained-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22People%20have%20been%20using%20ChatGPT%20and%20other%20AI%20tools%20to%20%26quot%3Bmanifest%26quot%3B%20their%20ideal%20lives.%20Now%20they're%20creating%20videos%2C%20too.%20I%20wasn't%20sure%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%20try.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22knotopoulos%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Notopoulos)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A