n-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20self-made%20millionaire%20says%20he%20doesn't%20believe%20in%20index%20funds%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20and%20explains%20why%20he%20doesn't%20see%20options%20as%20higher%20risk%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22478%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jason%20brown%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68890f803d5881a51c1e2f33%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22359%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrown%20and%20his%20family%20reside%20in%20Detroit.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jason%20Brown%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJason%20Brown%20rebuilt%20his%20wealth%20through%20options%20trading%20after%20early%20investment%20losses.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBrown's%20skepticism%20of%20traditional%20investing%20led%20him%20to%20focus%20on%20self-directed%20options.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20emphasizes%20understanding%20options%20to%20mitigate%20risk%20and%20protect%20financial%20assets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJason%20Brown%20built%20wealth%20his%20own%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20disappointing%20early%20experience%20handing%20over%20his%20money%20to%20professionals%20%E2%80%94%20he%20took%20%242%2C000%20worth%20of%20high%20school%20graduation%20money%20to%20the%20bank%20to%20invest%20and%2C%20two%20years%20later%2C%20his%20account%20had%20dropped%20to%20%24700%20%E2%80%94%20he%20decided%20if%20he%20was%20going%20to%20lose%20money%2C%20at%20least%20it%20would%20be%20on%20his%20own%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20college%20student%2C%20he%20started%20buying%20stocks%20and%20grew%20his%20modest%20savings%20to%20six%20figures%20before%20losing%20it%20all%20on%20one%20trade.%20After%20selling%20his%20car%2C%20moving%20back%20home%2C%20and%20taking%20a%20job%20at%20Verizon%20selling%20cellphones%2C%20he%20started%20trading%20again%20%E2%80%94%20this%20time%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foptions-trader-portfolio-stock-losses-7-figures-retail-investor-millionaire-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20set%20of%20investing%20principles%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20would%20prevent%20him%20from%20going%20broke%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%2C%2043%2C%20gradually%20rebuilt%20his%20portfolio%20and%20hit%20the%20seven-figure%20mark%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-options-trading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrading%20options%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Business%20Insider%20confirmed%20his%20net%20worth%20by%20reviewing%20an%20account%20summary%20that%20shows%20his%202024%20investment%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20option%20is%20a%20type%20of%20financial%20contract%20giving%20you%20the%20right%2C%20but%20not%20the%20obligation%2C%20to%20buy%20or%20sell%20an%20asset%20at%20a%20specific%20price%20before%20a%20specific%20date.%20Options%20are%20generally%20more%20complex%20than%20traditional%20investing%2C%20such%20as%20buying%20and%20holding%20stocks%20or%20index%20funds%2C%20but%20Brown's%20adamant%20that%20traditional%20investing%20doesn't%20cut%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20really%20believe%20in%20index%20funds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20became%20skeptical%20after%20digging%20into%20his%20401(k)%20plan%20when%20he%20worked%20for%20Verizon.%20Specifically%2C%20he%20looked%20at%20the%20fund%20his%20401(k)%20money%20was%20invested%20in.%20It%20was%20comprised%20of%20about%20five%20major%20companies%20like%20Apple%20and%20Google%20that%20he%20knew%20and%20trusted%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bthe%20rest%20of%20it%20was%20junk%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20when%20I%20was%20like%2C%20I%20want%20to%20move%20it%20over%20to%20a%20self-directed%20IRA%2C%20and%20I%20just%20want%20to%20pick%20these%20five%20companies.%20Why%20are%20they%20forcing%20me%20to%20buy%20all%20this%20other%20stuff%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findex-fund-investing-achieve-financial-independence-retire-early-build-wealth-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndex%20fund%20investing%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20helped%20many%20regular%20investors%20build%20wealth%2C%20but%20for%20Brown%2C%20who%20prefers%20to%20be%20more%20hands-on%20with%20his%20investments%2C%20options%20trading%20made%20more%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jason%20brown%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68826da2f748d8c055f63842%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22845%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrown%20dropped%20out%20of%20college%20to%20trade%20full-time.%20He%20eventually%20returned%20to%20Wayne%20State%20University%20and%20got%20his%20degree%20in%20finance.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jason%20Brown%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222d85c8ad-fc02-495c-a2b6-c46a0c418b28%5C%22%3E'Options%20are%20not%20risky.%20The%20way%20people%20use%20them%20is%20risky.'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%2C%20who%20trades%20full-time%2C%20runs%20a%20financial%20education%20company%2C%20and%20is%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffiveyearmillionaire.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFive-Year%20Millionaire%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20believes%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20misunderstanding%20around%20options%20trading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20people%20don't%20understand%20options%2C%20they'll%20say%2C%20'That's%20risky%20what%20he's%20doing.'%20The%20reality%20is%2C%20it's%20risky%20not%20knowing%20how%20to%20use%20options%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStock%20options%20can%20be%20compared%20to%20renters'%20or%20car%20insurance%2C%20depending%20on%20whether%20you're%20buying%20or%20selling%20options%20and%20whether%20you're%20using%20calls%20or%20puts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20buying%20a%20put%20is%20like%20buying%20car%20insurance.%20You%20pay%20a%20premium%20(the%20cost%20of%20the%20put)%2C%20and%20hope%20nothing%20bad%20happens%20(the%20stock%20doesn't%20crash)%2C%20but%20if%20it%20does%2C%20you're%20protected%3A%20You%20can%20sell%20the%20stock%20at%20the%20agreed-upon%20price%20(the%20strike%20price)%2C%20just%20like%20insurance%20would%20reimburse%20you%20if%20your%20car%20gets%20totaled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20options%20are%20so%20risky%2C%20then%20stop%20paying%20your%20homeowner's%20insurance%20or%20your%20car%20insurance%2C%20because%20that's%20what%20you're%20doing%20every%20month%20when%20you%20cut%20a%20check%3A%20You%20are%20buying%20a%20put%20option%20to%20protect%20yourself%20in%20case%20something%20happens%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Brown.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20don't%20we%20buy%20protection%20for%20our%20investment%20accounts%20when%20a%20COVID-19%20happens%2C%20when%20an%20'08%20real%20estate%20market%20crash%20happens%2C%20when%20a%20tariffs%20situation%20happens%2C%20and%20the%20market%20tanks%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOptions%20can%20require%20careful%20timing%20and%20market-watching%2C%20and%20Brown%20knows%20he%20won't%20make%20money%20on%20every%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20cannot%20be%20right%20on%20every%20trade%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20which%20is%20why%20he%20has%20a%20robust%20emergency%20fund%2C%20multiple%20revenue%20streams%2C%20and%20follows%20investing%20principles%2C%20including%3A%20Know%20your%20%26quot%3BI'm%20wrong%20level.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20lost%20everything%20in%20his%20early%2020s%2C%20he%20never%20considered%20his%20%26quot%3BI'm%20wrong%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%20%26quot%3BI%20only%20thought%2C%20'What%20would%20happen%20if%20this%20goes%20right%3F%20I'm%20getting%20a%20condo.'%20I%20never%20stopped%20to%20think%2C%20'If%20I'm%20wrong%2C%20I'll%20lose%20it%20all%20and%20I%20have%20to%20move%20back%20home.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20he%20knows%20exactly%20when%20he%20needs%20to%20cut%20his%20losses%20and%20shut%20down%2