tage%20on%20Tuesday%20of%20what%20it%20said%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-a-drone%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efirst-person-view%20attack%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20launched%20by%20boat%20crews%20on%20the%20open%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Main%20Intelligence%20Directorate%2C%20or%20GUR%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20its%20Telegram%20channel%20that%20the%20clips%20were%20archival%20footage%20of%20a%20raid%20on%20September%2011%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThanks%20to%20this%20component%20of%20the%20operation%2C%20the%20GUR%20soldiers%20were%20able%20to%20suppress%20enemy%20fire%20on%20the%20Petro%20Godovanets%20gas%20production%20platform%20in%20the%20Black%20Sea%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGUR%20said%20the%20attack%20was%20carried%20out%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-war-ukraine-began-crimea-could-end-there-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecoast%20of%20Crimea%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Raven%20Group%2C%20a%20unit%20in%20its%20special%20forces.%20Business%20Insider%20could%20not%20independently%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20footage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20clips%20appear%20to%20show%20a%20nighttime%20attack%2C%20where%20at%20least%20three%20first-person-view%2C%20or%20FPV%2C%20drones%20take%20off%20from%20a%20boat%20and%20crash%20into%20the%20ocean%20platform.%20Surveillance%20drone%20footage%20captured%20flashes%20and%20explosions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F-5pobZlAzaA%3Fsi%3DMiWg0M204ctCAoQr%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20occupier