rop%20that%20fits%20both%20the%20land%20and%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernment%20support%20has%20helped%20too.%20Farmers%20receive%20subsidies%20of%20%E2%82%B92000%20to%20%E2%82%B95000%20per%20kanal%20for%20planting%20material.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20even%20set%20up%20our%20own%20distillation%20unit.%20That%20increased%20our%20profits%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20a%20local%20farmer%20from%20Pulwama.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20still%20need%20better%20marketing%20channels%2C%20as%20seen%20in%20Doda%20or%20Kishtwar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20journey%20from%20experiment%20to%20movement%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20been%20working%20with%20lavender%20since%202015%20%E2%80%94%20you%20could%20say%20I%E2%80%99m%20emotionally%20connected%20to%20it%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ghulam%20Mohiudin%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Budgam.%20%E2%80%9CBack%20then%2C%20I%20spent%20around%20%E2%82%B98%2C000%20to%20%E2%82%B910%2C000%20per%20kanal.%20But%20once%20the%20crop%20bloomed%2C%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20feel%20like%20an%20expense%20at%20all%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20profitable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20even%20went%20to%20Delhi%20to%20buy%20books%20and%20learn%20everything%20%E2%80%94%20how%20it%E2%80%99s%20grown%2C%20how%20to%20care%20for%20it%2C%20and%20all%20the%20benefits.%20I%20started%20with%20just%20five%20or%20six%20kanals%2C%20but%20the%20interest%20kept%20growing%E2%80%A6%20now%20I%20farm%20over%2050%20kanals.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202490px)%20100vw%2C%202490px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FDSC_0994_11zon-1753453950.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222490%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Visitors%20at%20lavender%20farms%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FDSC_0994_11zon-17