%20team%20did%20a%20mapping%20exercise%20to%20identify%20high%20priority%20and%20low%20priority%20areas%20and%20where%20there%20is%20the%20highest%20amount%20of%20underutilised%20funds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-3_11zon-1753712301.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mapping%20DMFT%20funds%20revealed%20untapped%20resources%20that%20could%20be%20channelled%20to%20empower%20smallholder%20farmers.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-3_11zon-1753712301.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-3_11zon-1753712301-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-3_11zon-1753712301-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-3_11zon-1753712301-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-3_11zon-1753712301-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-477391%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMapping%20DMFT%20funds%20revealed%20untapped%20resources%20that%20could%20be%20channelled%20to%20empower%20smallholder%20farmers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mapping%20exercise%20revealed%20a%20crucial%20insight%3A%20%3Cstrong%3EDMFT%20funds%20could%20support%20smallholder%20farmers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20especially%20in%20regions%20where%20other%20public%20financing%20remained%20underutilised.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Horticulture%20was%20running%20promising%20programmes%20involving%20%3Cstrong%3Esolar-powered%20cold%20storages%20and%20dryers%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3