%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeedless%20to%20say%2C%20Kaziranga%E2%80%99s%20current%20avatar%20would%20surprise%20Gee.%20It%E2%80%99s%20spinning%20a%20success%20story%20across%20430%20sq%20km%2C%20playing%20host%20to%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20population%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F454940%2Fkaziranga-drones-protecting-rhinos%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eendangered%20Indian%20one-horned%20rhinoceros%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20swamp%20deer%2C%20large%20elephants%2C%20and%20a%20high%20density%20of%20tigers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20today%20is%20a%20UNESCO-approved%20verdant%20sprawl%20looked%20quite%20the%20opposite%20a%20century%20ago.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20behind%20the%20makeover%20is%20Mahi%20Chandra%20Miri%2C%20whose%20story%20will%20remain%20a%20page-turner%20in%20the%20annals%20of%20conservation%20history.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20life%20and%20times%20of%20Mahi%20Miri%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20wooden%20signboard%20five%20kilometres%20east%20of%20the%20Bagori%20sub-beat%20forest%20office%20at%20the%20Kaziranga%20National%20Park%20reads%20in%20bold%20font%2C%20%E2%80%98Mahi%20Miri%20Tower%E2%80%99.%20An%20arrow%20directs%20you%20to%20a%20hillock%2C%20where%20the%20conservationist%20spent%20many%20an%20evening%20keeping%20watch%20on%20the%20forested%20land%20(in%20those%20days%2C%20its%20identity%20was%20that%20of%20a%20game%20sanctuary).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20vantage%20point%20offered%20him%20sweeping%20views%20of%20the%20forest%3B%20he%E2%80%99d%20be%20quick%20to%20notice%20any%20skulduggery%3B%20the%20sanctuary%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F463429%2Fandaman-24x7-forest-station-wildlife-crime-deer-wild-pigs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enotorious%20for%20poaching%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%2