nivas-new-york-germany%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EColours%20were%20extracted%20from%20natural%20sources%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20stone%2C%20earth%2C%20conch%20shells%2C%20and%20soot%2C%20then%20mixed%20by%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20the%20arrival%20of%20modern%20media%20in%20the%2020th%20century%2C%20including%20books%2C%20newspapers%2C%20radio%2C%20and%20film%2C%20the%20role%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EPatua%3C%2Fem%3E%20diminished.%20People%20no%20longer%20gathered%20for%20scroll%20performances%20as%20they%20once%20had.%20Traditional%20patrons%20disappeared.%20Without%20demand%2C%20many%20artists%20were%20forced%20to%20abandon%20their%20craft.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20late%201900s%2C%20Pattachitra%20had%20become%2C%20in%20many%20places%2C%20a%20shadow%20of%20itself.%20What%20was%20once%20central%20to%20storytelling%20and%20social%20exchange%20was%20now%20considered%20a%20fading%20folk%20curiosity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-28T080531.046_11zon-1753670148.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pattachitra%20lived%20not%20just%20in%20the%20brush%2C%20but%20in%20memory%2C%20inherited%20through%20families%20like%20folklore%20itself%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Gaatha%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-28T080531.046_11zon-1753670148.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-28T080531.046_11zon-1753670148-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-28T080